summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Utah Street from Connecticut Street to Atlantic Street; and Atlantic Street from Utah Street to Railroad Avenue in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 12819, creating Local Improvement District No. 1126 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
